Z","msg":"抵啦坡狗，英国人保家衛族何罪之有"},{"pid":"09266941446e0f04b6409bc96a0f6cc6d0f7c173","tid":1912714,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f01a9055a3263eef72756951c60ba6de6708fb3","tid":1912714,"uid":85629,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:36:00.000Z","msg":"坡狗總理講嘢未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f69bec6b3815704d9e4d65f12297c0dfaa0622e","tid":1912714,"uid":309935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"32ae1e24aebb7a210cfc537c97e48c68066b4679","tid":1912714,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:10:10.000Z","msg":"呢單野仲要回幾多次帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09fb0e09a101bf4a75c05673c75dff139828d2b","tid":1912714,"uid":216664,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:01:11.000Z","msg":"在英港人Write in Hongkonger UK: <br />\nMake Hongkongers count in the 2021 UK census<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aDqMJGXupn4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaDqMJGXupn4&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=78bc1efd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aDqMJGXupn4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1926928/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1926928/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n現今大部份人都會填 Asian or Asian British: Chinese<br />\n2021，我在英香港人地要填 Asian or Asian British: Other Asian，記得 specify &ldquo;Hongkonger&quot;"},{"pid":"86bc764b6d2074c3d3981c6149b2c60bb1085a2d","tid":1912714,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:29:00.000Z","msg":"白人抗疫又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果然係世上最偉大既人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靠白人救港了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c0b2f07d832109fad0d7d17678e2c739a30805","tid":1912714,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/v0gy0cic5bzonwl/status/1239189294700363777?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fv0gy0cic5bzonwl%2Fstatus%2F1239189294700363777%3Fs%3D21&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=7baba552\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fv0gy0cic5bzonwl%2Fstatus%2F1239189294700363777%3Fs%3D21&h=19bc6c1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/v0gy0cic5bzonwl/status/1239189294700363777?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n［突發］有人整左維尼病毒公仔出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1926864\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1926864</a></blockquote>"}]}